Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2B2490&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider's Finisher Training
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}No hunting{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! Did you think\Nyou could outrun me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but GOD's test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream Virus, away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting now, you'll work\Nfor GOD as human robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now go back to your daily\Nlives until further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I miss one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After them! Hunt them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, you have to go on alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let her be alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman, are you the only one who escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to speak,\NI'll just have to make you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Daughter Miki... Bottom of cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck are you?\NA friend of the X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to take out the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles, they should call\Nyou the Instant Kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant Kettle?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You heat up in no time.\NThat's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your weakness, Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that guy!? After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles, how is the Dream Virus taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment's a total\Nsuccess, Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dream Virus will be ready\Nfor mass-production in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep it hidden until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, don't take your\Neyes off the X Rider. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still one loose end left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find that missing\Ngirl and shut her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How's my time, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it one more lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my dream to train\Na Grand Prix racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongou Takeshi, Ichimonji Hayato,\NKazami Shirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Any of those three could\Nhave been champion for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But they've scattered across the\Nworld to protect justice and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Jin Keisuke...\NHe has the potential to be even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But he has his own evils to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Keisuke?\NSomething happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl suddenly walked\Nout in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She did!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, little lady!\NLittle lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's had a terrible shock.\NMight even have lost her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get her to a hospital quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency transmission: Missing girl\Nfound. Jin Keisuke's got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'll draw them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, you die today...\Nwith that girl you saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're not just after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Toubei, hand over\Nthe girl if you want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A GOD monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This car's going sixty!\NWhat are you doing at the window!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My feet can keep up with a jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Try chasing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Toubei, it's no\Nuse running. Join GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here, X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One of GOD's monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And they named me Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran off, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, GOD's after this girl.\NShe must know some secret of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to help her\Nregain her memory, and soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you interfere!?\NI know you're hiding up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? You with GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your mission, Achilles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your primary objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it to turn all Japan's people\Ninto robots with the Dream Virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd lost to the\NX Rider just now, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd lose to him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blood goes to your head\Ntoo fast. That's your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where have I heard that before...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm yourself. Then dispose\Nof that girl called Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask this girl's parents, relatives, or\Nanyone who knows her to come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact Coffee Shop COL\Nin Ikuta, Tama Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, that's Ikuta, Tama Ward--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's broadcasts like\Nthat on the TV and radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's bound to come asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll remember everything you forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This dart that nearly hit you\Nis coated with a weird liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having it analysed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird liquid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So this dart's the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A dart like that gave her the shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, give her a closer look!\NShe might remember something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No... We should play it safe\Nuntil she calms down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, stop crying. It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki! Miki, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who might you be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was driving Miki, turned away\Nfor a second, and she was gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, Jin Keisuke...\NI was right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... Let's give this girl the\Nsame treatment as her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! Help, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, settle down.\NI'm your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're not my dad!\NYou're the monster who hurt the villagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've regained your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll join your mother and the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've given\Nup the daddy act.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a bit of a risk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miki's regained her\Nmemory thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon Miki, Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl, Miki.\NHide somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Big Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere, Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interfering!\NFight, Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Miki might--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll fall to Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you dawdling?\NHurry up and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright... Withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days until\NOperation: Dream Virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cursed X Rider...\NLet's see you recover by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Keisuke?\NHang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD took Miki away\Nright in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't lift a finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of\Nbeing the X Rider!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've tasted failure for\Nthe first time in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief... Will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The three Kamen Riders\Nwho came before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they do\Nat times like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men are outstanding\Nheroes of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd fail, and fail again,\Nand stand up again every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing up after every loss\Nis what makes a Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm... I'm still\NKamen Rider X...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't use their\Ntitle if I just complain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped Riders #1, #2, and V3\Nout of a few pinches too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Double Punch,\Nthe Midair Kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They mastered new finishing moves\Nby risking their lives in training!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, it's time for the X Rider\Nto start his Finisher Training!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief... I'll do it!\NYou can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes you the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Training starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This fires blanks, but they'll\Nstill leave a mark! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow! You're a sitting\Nduck in midair!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fate of a Kamen Rider.\NGood luck, X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider had been overwhelmed by\NApollo Geist and Achilles' attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Would this training yield\Na new finishing move?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's plan to turn the Japanese\Ninto robots will soon unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X has started training to\Ndevelop a new finishing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The training is harsh and strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'll complete it with\NTachibana Toubei's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week, you'll see\Nthe X Rider's new finisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"GOD Secret Police! Apollo Geist!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider